           perform   prn-rou-pri-840      thru prn-rou-pri-841        .
           perform   prn-rou-pri-850      thru prn-rou-pri-851        .
           move      w-cnt-prn-sav-rot    to   w-rot                  .
           perform   prn-rou-pri-750      thru prn-rou-pri-751        .
